{
  "title": "ISic003079. I.Sicily inscription 003079",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δέκο\n                    με\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δέκο\n                    με\"><span data-text=\"Δέκο\n                    με\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Δέκομος\">[Δ]έκο-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>με</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖ\n                    ρε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ρε</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Δέκομε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Δέκομος\">Δέκομε</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δέκο\n                    με\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δέκο\n                    με\"><span data-text=\"Δέκο\n                    με\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Δέκομος\">[.]ΕΚΟ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΜΕ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"χαῖ\n                    ρε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΡΕ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Δέκομε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Δέκομος\">ΔΕΚΟΜΕ</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003079_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo M. Metcalfe\" src=\"ISic003079_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003079.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo M. Metcalfe\" src=\"ISic003079-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Isler 1988</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Farewell Dekomos</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Dekomos is presumably Decimus, and is attested in other Sicilian greek inscriptions, such as <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002952\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002952</a> (Cefalu), and as Dekomia at Syracuse in <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000841\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000841</a></p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 38.0932 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Isler 1987 12 with fig.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002490\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002490</a>  </li><li> Isler 1988 23-24 tav.4.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001913\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001913</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Lunate epsilon</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
