      "html": "<h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Dekomos is presumably Decimus, and is attested in other Sicilian greek inscriptions, such as <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002952\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002952</a> (Cefalu), and as Dekomia at Syracuse in <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000841\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000841</a></p>  "
